
Install qdarkstyle with pip by using following command

pip install qdarkstyle

look for mainwindow.py under C:\ProgramData\Anaconda3\Lib\site-packages\spyder\app

Add following command

import qdarkstyle

search for class MainWindow , def __init__ and add following 

self.setStyleSheet(qdarkstyle.load_stylesheet_pyqt5())

save mainwindow.py file and restart spyder 

change syntax coloring to spyder dark tools --> preferences --> syntax coloring
